snippet.title: Rope'n'Fly 4 (Official Preview Trailer)
snippet.description:
Rope’n’Fly 4 now available for Android FOR FREE! We are very proud to announce this sequel to one of our best selling games, Rope’n’Fly. Join million of players now, give it a try, you will love it!

Android: http://bit.ly/1BV4VFk
iOS: coming early September 2014
Amazon: coming early September 2014

Djinnworks on the
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/robert-szeleney/id302877209?mt=8
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Djinnworks+e.U.
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Djinnworks
Website: http://www.djinnworks.at
